{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_06_01",
  "title": "伊吹渚 1話 理想のクリスマスデート",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "失礼します、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "早いな渚。どうしたんだ？　新曲のジャケット撮影の\n打ち合わせの時間まで、まだ二時間もあるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're early‚ Nagisa. What's up? We still have two hours\nbefore the new song's cover photoshoot meeting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、午前中のお仕事が凄くスムーズにいって\n予定より早く上がれたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ my morning work went really smoothly‚\nso I finished earlier than planned.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、新曲の撮影が楽しみ過ぎて\nつい早く来ちゃいました……えへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got so excited about the new song's photoshoot\nthat I came here early… Hehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、じゃあお茶でも飲んで\nゆっくりしていてくれ……はぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Well then‚ let's have some tea‚\nand relax for a bit… sigh",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "？　{user}さん、どうしたんですか？\n元気がないみたいですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ what's wrong?\nYou seem a bit down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "年末でお忙しいのは分かりますけど\nちゃんとお休みも取って下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand that you're busy at the year-end‚\nbut please make sure to take some time off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "元気がないように見えるか？\n表情には出さないようにしてたんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do I really look down?\nI've been trying not to show it on my face‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの、すぐに分かりますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can tell right away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "だって、ずっと{user}さんと\n仕事してきたんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After all‚ I've been working with\n{user}-san for so long.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "表情には出さなくても\n仕草とか雰囲気でなんとなく分かっちゃうんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if you don't express it on your face‚\nI can kind of tell from your gestures and vibes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "人のことをよく見てるんだな。渚らしいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're quite observant‚ Nagisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "話してみて下さい。私、相談に乗りますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Try talking to me. I'm here to listen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。でも、これは俺の仕事の問題だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ but this is a work-related issue‚ so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "そうやって、なんでも抱え込むのはダメですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You shouldn't try to handle everything on your own like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは、一人で頑張ろうと\nし過ぎるって、琴乃ちゃんも心配してました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan is worried about you\nbecause you tend to do things alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはいつも私達を\n助けてくれるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since {user}-san have always been there to help us‚\nwe want to be a source of strength",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "私達だって、力になりたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "for you too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった。じゃあ、聞いてくれるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Alright. Then‚ will you listen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "実は、ついさっき星見プロのアイドルの特集ページを\n組みたいって、つてのある出版社から連絡があったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I just received a call from a publishing company that\nthey want to feature the idols of Hoshimi Prods. in a special section.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "いいお話だと思いますけど……\nどうして、そんなに浮かない顔をしてるんです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That sounds like a great opportunity…\nWhy do you look so unhappy about it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "取材と撮影のスケジュールが急過ぎるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The schedule for interviews and photoshoots is too tight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "急過ぎるって……いつなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Too tight… When is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "来週の頭なんだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's at the beginning of next week.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　確かに急過ぎますよね\n何か事情でもあるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!? That is really sudden.\nIs there some reason for this rush?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "当初予定していた他の事務所のアイドルが急病らしい\nでも、この企画に合う代役が見つからないって話で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems an idol from another agency who was initially planned got suddenly ill‚\nbut they can't find a suitable replacement for this project…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "うちも、みんな年末のスケジュールは空いてない\nでも、相手は以前お世話になった人なんだよな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And all of us here are already booked for year-end activities‚\nbut the person they want is someone I have a history with……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "だから断り辛いんですね\n{user}さん、優しいから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why it's hard to decline\nas {user}-san is kind-hearted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "力にはなりたいけど、みんなに無理はさせられない\nだから申し訳ないけど、断わろうかと思ってるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to help‚ but I can't push everyone too hard.\nSo‚ I'm thinking about turning it down‚ although I feel sorry about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.6333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、{user}さん\n私じゃ……ダメですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ {user}-san‚\nWhat if… it's me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "来週の頭だったら、ちょうどオフが一日ありますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next week‚ I have a day off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
